	<!-- TEXT  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A Cure For All Ills</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_HELP">
			<Text>Cloaked figures await you in the antechamber, Your Greatness. I think they wish to discuss... the Fountain.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permenantly yields +1 [ICON_FOOD] Food, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The Fountain's waters are distributed via Aqueducts, Baths and Grocers. All these buildings yield +3 [ICON_FOOD] Food.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The Fountain loses up to -10 [ICON_FOOD] Food. A Cathedral is erected atop the ruins, and 75% of the City converts to your majority religion.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Nearby Farms provide +2 [ICON_FOOD] Food; this effect has a Maintenance of -5 [ICON_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Whether you believe it's magic or all in their heads, there is no doubt that the so-called 'Fountain of Youth' has a noticable effect on those who imbibe from its waters. We shall continue funding the... err... organisation.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*The envoys wish to warn us of the dangers of opening up the fountain to the public*[NEWLINE]While we appreciate the gentlemen's position on security, it strikes me that the waters of the fountain could be distributed - at least locally - without anyone being strictly aware of it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The cloaked figures reveal themselves as priests! They demand the destruction of this pagan shrine!*[NEWLINE]Damn, they found out. I suppose we can bury the fountain in exchange for certain assurances of the church.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_FOUNTAIN_YOUTH_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*The secret society is very happy with the previous policy of distributing the well's waters in... well, secret. They wish to roll the scheme out to farmland irrigation*[NEWLINE]Excellent. I'm glad they see our way of thinking at last.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
